MatPat CHOKES in Megaman ►► X http://bit.ly/20TVSzY
Kaizo Mario: Death Awaits (Part 1) ►► http://bit.ly/1WO6pdK

Jumping back into retro platforming with one of my all time faves - MEGA MAN! MegaMan Unlimited to be exact. A game created by fans, for fans. Let's put my platforming skills to the test in this lost chapter of the Mega Man story.
